Google, along with Yahoo! and MSN, participates in [[China]]'s [[internet censorship]] program, commonly referred to as the [[Great Firewall of China]]. The Chinese version of Google, www.google.cn, limits search results on such topics as the [[Tiananmen Square Massacre]], and other topics considered off-limits by Chinese authorities. See [[History of Google]] for for more information regarding this controversy.
